{
  "$Comment": "Boss-capstone role template for the corrupted-Kweebec Warden. Cloned from Template_KweebecNightmare_Blight (the proven hostile Kweebec spear AI that already chases relentlessly in this arena, with huge sight/alerted/hearing ranges and the de-leashed pursuit), adapted for a multi-phase BOSS: it adds UseCombatActionEvaluator + a _CombatConfig param (the Goblin_Duke pattern) and a Burn param (mirrors Goblin_Duke_Phase_3) so each phase Variant can flip them. The three phase Variants (KweebecNightmare_Warden / _Phase2 / _Phase3) differ by MaxHealth, _CombatConfig, and Burn. Phase SWAPS are driven from Java (boss/BossController) on HP thresholds, NOT a self-driving ActionRole, because this role does not replicate the Goblin_Duke arena prefab-path instruction tree (Throne/Arena markers) that the native ActionRole/TriggerSpawnBeacon mechanics depend on. SPIKE: verify UseCombatActionEvaluator coexists with the inherited Razorleaf AttackSequence instruction tree in-game; if the CAE conflicts, drop UseCombatActionEvaluator and let the inherited spear combat carry the fight (the Blight already fights correctly without a CAE).",
